headline: Lockheed Martin Secures $509M Contract for GPS III Satellite Program
summary: On May 28, Lockheed Martin Corporation (NYSE:LMT) secured a $509.76 million contract modification from the U.S. Air Force for the development of GPS III Follow-On Space Vehicles 21 and 22, increasing the total contract value to $4.1 billion. This contract builds upon Lockheed Martin’s ongoing work with GPS III satellites. The project features advanced anti-jamming […]
